<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-157] Unexpected exception when sending a SOAPFault on soap12</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-157</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you try to create a fault using the makefault and specifying the soap version to be soap12 Rampart throws and unexpected exception of invlid soap fault.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See the following thread for the configurations and the stack trace; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/Access-to-validation-error-message-tf4498668.html#a13284520&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/Access-to-validation-error-message-tf4498668.html#a13284520&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
